{"id": 1953, "genre": 1001, "title": "你看穿了哪些塑造“理想生活方式”的套路？", "description": "天天被教“你应该这么活”，你也一样有点烦恼吗？", "record_count": 2737, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171012110020pFlhMJQVbYenRkmw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-13T03:00:03Z", "options": [{"id": 241920, "content": "多读书，读好书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806190}, {"id": 249603, "content": "不是所有人都能活得像明星，天天换装，天天化妆的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186502}, {"id": 241672, "content": "叫我买买买的基本上都是套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}, {"id": 241682, "content": "并不想按照别人的理想生活！?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138165}, {"id": 242194, "content": "大家都说万事万物皆有一个度，运动也是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147470}, {"id": 241684, "content": "咳咳   我与贵报的三观  很契合啊！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154866}, {"id": 241685, "content": "二线员工:被上级洗脑还要想着怎么洗脑下级", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92953}, {"id": 241687, "content": "熬过这段时间就好了，可结果的结果是日复一日，年复一年再回头看，你的一生是多么无趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154871}, {"id": 241689, "content": "健身难道和意志力没关吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766691}, {"id": 241434, "content": "有钱就该到处去耍，到出去耍的人都有钱。有钱又到处去耍的人都幸福。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979879}, {"id": 241435, "content": "各种刷旅行的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911176}, {"id": 241436, "content": "消费升级，你才能升级（放屁，就是惦记我兜里的三块两毛！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296008}, {"id": 241693, "content": "绝大多数在网络媒介上展示的理想生活都是经过隐藏和包装之后，引来一群人无知的艳羡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150808}, {"id": 241439, "content": "文字多的话没有显示全呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475848}, {"id": 241956, "content": "（真的， 不是某些视频弹幕里刷防不胜防的那种）防不胜防  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014928}, {"id": 242982, "content": "生活不止眼前的苟且，还有远方的诗和田野", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958420}, {"id": 241447, "content": "房子买了吗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106579}, {"id": 241448, "content": "勇敢點！反正聽話也不會得到幸福～", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154042}, {"id": 241449, "content": "我想我之所以喜欢好奇心日报，就是因为你们这样不甘被所谓理想生活套路的人在这里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013083}, {"id": 241450, "content": "大学生必做的50件事…", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154057}, {"id": 242986, "content": "我想做高级咸鱼不是高级精英", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161604}, {"id": 241451, "content": "想做的事太多，发现只能在每夜转点时抱怨今天似乎什么也没做成", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147430}, {"id": 241452, "content": "DO WHAT U WANT TO DO ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154008}, {"id": 241454, "content": "品牌即身份，大概是世界上最大的营销谎言", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761362}, {"id": 241455, "content": "“生活不止眼前的苟且，还有诗和远方的田野”。没有眼前的苟且，哪儿来远方的田野？", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598759}, {"id": 241458, "content": "男主外，女主内。家务孩子就该是女人的事儿，男人怎么能进厨房呢…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866878}, {"id": 241715, "content": "要坚持", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154931}, {"id": 241716, "content": "深色衣物要与浅色衣物分开洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154931}, {"id": 241462, "content": "生活不止有眼前的苟且，还有诗和远方（的苟且）", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730742}, {"id": 241463, "content": "比如大方地夹杂在新闻里的软广，这种渗透式的，被生活的生活方式我不喜欢，但其实没啥反抗的余地……?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154108}, {"id": 241464, "content": "生活不止眼前的苟且，还有远方的诗和田野（抱歉，眼前就已经够我努力应对了）", "image": "img/option/option/20171013153455ODb4cUMkLG0Bh961", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955239}, {"id": 241721, "content": "钻石恒久远，一颗永流传。\n一种没有任何实用价值的石头居然代表了爱情婚姻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154947}, {"id": 241466, "content": "各种文章提到成功，可到底怎样算是成功？只有腰缠万贯才算吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147717}, {"id": 241978, "content": "每个女生都需要一台美颜相机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112418}, {"id": 241467, "content": "好的生活没那么贵 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244502}, {"id": 241468, "content": "何以解忧，唯有暴富", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714607}, {"id": 241469, "content": "说这些的\n要么坏\n要么蠢\n\n信这些的\n要么愚\n要么就是自己骗自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130359}, {"id": 241470, "content": "什么是幸福生活，一家三口加上一条金毛还有吉普车的中产阶级生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148662}, {"id": 241471, "content": "钻石骗局和提前消费（信用卡）卡奴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531507}, {"id": 241473, "content": "社会主义好", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092852}, {"id": 241729, "content": "神烦别人指指点点", "image": "img/option/option/20171014190012vWlnSG8wR1P7QCYh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196496}, {"id": 241474, "content": "看着不错哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154171}, {"id": 241730, "content": "只能嫁个老实人....老实人招你惹你了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898457}, {"id": 241475, "content": "什么逃离北上广深，去过幸福美满向往的生活，简直可笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119626}, {"id": 241476, "content": "所有理想都归为套路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097303}, {"id": 241478, "content": "各种城市化的“高级”生活方式。各种服装穿搭案例，好像除了不那样穿就土爆了。各种居家搭配案例，我东西会找不到好嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154200}, {"id": 241479, "content": "信用卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 241735, "content": "双眼皮才好看 高鼻梁才好看 鹅蛋脸才好看 又高又瘦才好看 黄金比例才好看 大众审美人人都长得一样到底哪里好看？？？ （可不可以收藏这个专题 真的很喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638550}, {"id": 241991, "content": "那些告诉你怎么活的人，没一个过得好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149379}, {"id": 241480, "content": "给人一种很有钱，很有品味，很能掌控自己一切的印象", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}]}